## 🚀 Quick Start (Local)

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.11+
- A modern browser (Chrome / Firefox / Edge)

### 1. Install dependencies

```bash
cd cornlab-public
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Start the backend

```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000
```

### 3. Open the game

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/app
```

The SQLite database (`cornlab.db`) is created automatically on first run.
Interactive API docs are available at `http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs`.

---

## ☁️ Production Deployment

### Frontend → Cloudflare Pages

1. Go to [pages.cloudflare.com](https://pages.cloudflare.com) → Create a project
2. Connect this GitHub repository
3. Set build settings:
   - **Build command:** *(leave empty)*
   - **Build output directory:** `frontend`
4. Deploy — Cloudflare gives you `https://cornlab.pages.dev`

### Backend → Railway

1. Go to [railway.app](https://railway.app) → New Project → Deploy from GitHub
2. Connect this repository — Railway auto-detects `railway.toml`
3. Add a **PostgreSQL** addon (sets `DATABASE_URL` automatically)
4. Set environment variables:

| Variable | Value |
|----------|-------|
| `DATABASE_URL` | Auto-set by Railway PostgreSQL addon |
| `ALLOWED_ORIGIN` | `https://your-site.pages.dev` |

### Configure the API URL

Edit `frontend/js/config.js` — the only file you need to change:

```js
const CONFIG = {
  API_BASE: "https://your-backend.up.railway.app/api",
};
```

Push to GitHub — both platforms redeploy automatically.

See [`DEPLOY.md`](./DEPLOY.md) for the complete step-by-step guide.

---

## 🔌 API Reference

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/users/create` | Create or retrieve a user |
| GET | `/api/users/{id}` | Get user profile, XP, badges |
| POST | `/api/sessions/start` | Start a new game session |
| POST | `/api/sessions/{id}/end` | End a session |
| POST | `/api/game/sample` | Draw random sample + run t-test |
| POST | `/api/game/decide` | Submit H₀ decision, receive result |
| POST | `/api/game/reveal` | Reveal true field heatmap |
| POST | `/api/actions/log` | Log a player action event |
| POST | `/api/test/submit` | Submit post-test answers |
| GET | `/api/analytics/summary` | Aggregate accuracy + error rates |
| GET | `/api/analytics/export/csv` | Download all results as CSV |

---

## 📊 Database Schema

| Table | Key Fields |
|-------|-----------|
| `users` | username, group (A/B), xp, level, badges |
| `sessions` | user_id, chapter, started_at, ended_at, seed |
| `actions` | session_id, action_type, payload, timestamp |
| `results` | chapter, h0_accepted, correct, type1_error, type2_error, sample_mean, time_spent_sec, hint_count, retry_count, journal_text |
| `pretests` | user_id, test_type (pre/post), answers, score |

Export all results to CSV:
```
GET /api/analytics/export/csv
```

