## 🎓 Chapter Overview

| # | Title | True Mean | H₀ Mean | Key Concept |
|---|-------|-----------|---------|-------------|
| 1 | The Suspicious Harvest | 50.0 bu | 50.0 bu | Guided tutorial, cannot fail |
| 2 | The Claim | 52.0 bu | 50.0 bu | Basic hypothesis test |
| 3 | Conflicting Data | 48.5 bu | 50.0 bu | Noisy data, borderline p-value |
| 4 | The Storm | 53.0 bu | 50.0 bu | High variance, wide CI |
| 5 | The Policy Decision | 49.0 bu | 50.0 bu | High-stakes, subtle effect |

---

## 🧪 Research Design

### Metrics Collected
- Decision accuracy per chapter
- Type I error rate (false alarm — rejected true H₀)
- Type II error rate (missed effect — accepted false H₀)
- Time spent per chapter
- Hint usage count
- Retry count per chapter
- Journal text length
- Post-test score

### Reproducibility
All field data is generated from a fixed random seed (default: `42`). Change the seed per session for variation across participants.

